data.name: label4.Text
data.value: Do you need a place to hold meetings for your club, work, or hobby group? Do you want to throw an open mic night, networking event, team celebration, or product launch? Or perhaps you're arranging a birthday or anniversary celebration? For all of your gathering requirements, Together Culture is the ideal location. To make your event special and encourage a sense of community among your guests, Together Culture may offer team building and creative skills workshops, ranging from design thinking to butter churning, upon request. Together Culture's goal is to support Cambridge's creative economy in its transition to a more sustainable and inclusive sector. The launch of our Citizens' Studio and systems change incubator, which aims to put ideas into action, will be supported by the profits from place rental.
